---
title: About
description: Learn more about Wheeldogg
---

{% extends "@includes/layout.twig" %}

{% block body %}
<main class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Image placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500/20 to-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-violet-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-5xl font-bold">
          W
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-brand-400 font-medium mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide text-sm">About Me</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
          Hey, I'm <span class="gradient-text">Wheeldogg</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="prose lg:prose-lg">
          <p>
            I'm a creator living at the intersection of technology and art.
            My days are split between writing code, producing music, exploring
            the outdoors, and capturing it all through photography and drone footage.
          </p>
          <p>
            I believe that creativity flows between disciplines - the patterns
            I find in code echo in music, the peace I find in nature fuels my
            creativity, and staying physically fit keeps my mind sharp for all of it.
          </p>
          <p>
            This blog is my space to share that journey. You'll find tutorials,
            project breakdowns, nature adventures, fitness insights, and plenty
            of visual content from my explorations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="category-badge bg-violet-500/10 text-violet-400">Music Producer</span>
          <span class="category-badge bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400">Developer</span>
          <span class="category-badge bg-green-500/10 text-green-400">Nature Lover</span>
          <span class="category-badge bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-400">Fitness Enthusiast</span>
          <span class="category-badge bg-rose-500/10 text-rose-400">Photographer</span>
          <span class="category-badge bg-sky-500/10 text-sky-400">Drone Pilot</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Skills/Interests Grid -->
    <div class="mt-20">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-12">What Drives Me</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-violet-400">Music & Sound</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">
            From electronic production to acoustic experimentation, I'm fascinated
            by how sound shapes our emotions and experiences. I produce, mix, and
            constantly explore new sonic territories.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-cyan-400">Software & Code</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">
            Building things with code is deeply satisfying. Whether it's web
            applications, automation tools, or creative coding projects, I love
            solving problems through technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-400">Nature & Outdoors</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">
            There's nothing like being out in nature to reset and recharge.
            Hiking, camping, and simply being present in natural spaces is
            essential to my creative process.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-400">Fitness & Movement</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400">
            Staying active isn't just about physical health - it's about mental
            clarity and pushing limits. Training consistently is a cornerstone
            of how I approach everything else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
{% endblock %}
